ratom(X) or ratom(Stream,X)

     The next lexical token on the current or specified input stream is bound
     to X.  eg,

                  : ratom(X)?
                  > fred

                  X = fred.

                  : ratom(X)?
                  > 123

                  X = 123         % X is an integer

                  : ratom(X)?
                  > <=

                  X = '<='

                  : ratom(X)?
                  > ,

                  X = ','
